Introduce_detail: Green era is one of the pioneers in the field of banana fiber fashion production, committed to providing banana fiber fashion products that are friendly to people and the environment. Committed to minimizing environmental impacts throughout the supply chain, from raw materials, production processes, to transportation and packaging. Using recycled, organic or sustainably sourced materials, and implementing measures to reduce carbon emissions.
Core_value_detail: + Providing sustainable and environmentally friendly products.
Core_value_detail_2: + Prioritizing innovation and creativity: Always looking for new methods and technologies to optimize production and improve the quality of green products.
Core_value_detail_3: + Strive to develop production and raise customer awareness of the importance of sustainable fashion, thereby promoting a green lifestyle.
Vision_detail: To become a leading brand in the sustainable fashion industry, leading the global green fashion trend, where every product is a symbol of the perfect combination of style, quality and responsibility to the environment and society.
Mission_detail: We are committed to bringing the highest quality banana fiber fashion products, we want to create long-term values ​​for customers, contribute to protecting the planet and building a green future for future generations.
Commitment_detail_1: With a passion for a green fashion industry, we are committed to bringing customers truly new and friendly experiences when using products made from high-quality natural fabrics, banana fiber, not only a natural fabric friendly to the skin and environment, but banana fiber also has outstanding characteristics, breathable, sweat-absorbing, antibacterial and deodorizing, especially comfortable and benign.
Commitment_detail_2: Cherishing natural resources, valuing human health, wishing to contribute positively to the green fashion industry, Green Era was founded with a desire to participate in the global green supply chain, for a sustainable future.
picture_p: Positive impact on the environment and the garment industry.
picture_p_1: Every year, Vietnam has about 2,000 hectares of banana trees cut down - after harvesting the fruit, equivalent to 360 thousand tons of fiber and equivalent to 27 thousand billion. Green era, when solving the problem of waste from banana trees, not only increases the income of banana farmers but also solves the problem of agricultural by-products that are very valuable to the environment, especially creating a new and unique type of organic fiber for the green fashion industry.
commit_h1: LEADING SUPPLIER OF NATURAL AND SUSTAINABLE PRODUCTS
commit_p: With a passion for a green fashion industry, we are committed to bringing customers truly new, friendly experiences when using high-end natural fabric products – fabric made from banana fiber. This fabric is not only natural and skin-friendly but also environmentally friendly, with outstanding properties such as breathability, moisture absorption, antibacterial, deodorizing, particularly comfortable, and gentle on the skin.
commit_p_1: Valuing natural resources and prioritizing human health, with a desire to contribute positively to the green fashion industry, Green Era was founded with a vision to participate in the global green supply chain – for a sustainable future.

Content ct: Established on March 12, 2010, specializing in the production of chemical additives for concrete in the construction industry. With expertise from leading domestic and international experts in construction chemicals, combined with advanced technology from the Federal Republic of Germany, we continuously research and develop BMQ-branded concrete additives.
Core_Value_content1: Establishing close, sustainable, and trustworthy relationships with customers.
Core_Value_content2: Providing professional service and ensuring value for customers.
Core_Value_content3: Constantly striving and innovating in our work to deliver high-quality products and services at the most reasonable prices for customers.

Mission_content2: Providing professional service and ensuring value for customers.

About_content1: First of all, BMQ Production and Trading Joint Stock Company would like to extend our most respectful greetings to your esteemed company and sincerely thank you for your interest in our products.
About_content2: BMQ Production and Trading Joint Stock Company was established on March 12, 2010, specializing in the production of concrete chemical additives for the construction industry. With the expertise of leading domestic and international specialists in the construction chemicals sector and advanced technology from the Federal Republic of Germany, we have continuously researched and developed products under the "BMQ Concrete Admixture" brand.
About_content3: With a commitment to credibility and quality as the sustainable value of our products, we have continuously enhanced our skills to build a policy for BMQ concrete admixtures—products recognized by international organizations for their quality, environmental friendliness, and industrial safety.
About_content4: BMQ admixture products are registered in compliance with Vietnamese quality standards ISO 9001:2015, meeting TCVN 8826:2011 – Chemical Admixtures for Concrete, as well as international standard ASTM C494. The products have been tested and evaluated for quality at accredited laboratories and have proven their effectiveness in large-scale projects both nationally and globally.
About_content5: With the principle of prioritizing c ustomer benefits and affirming our brand through product quality, we also provide a team of technical experts who directly visit construction sites to collaborate with contractors during the mixing process, ensuring the most optimal solutions that meet all specific customer requirements.
About_content6: With our capabilities and experience, we hope to receive your attention and support. We firmly believe that BMQ concrete admixtures will always be a reputable product and a trusted companion for all our valued customers.
